ki Henya、 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@omurice_shokudo/featured" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Omuraisu Shokudo</strong></a>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UClWFwzCosFg76rM6iUhFsIA" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Sayo Nanashino</strong></a> <strong>，</strong>实现了前往动作捕捉工作室拍摄的梦想。最近，个人VTuber已经可以租用工作室并拍摄高质量的视频，但使用费并不便宜，而且需要花费大量的精力来准备。毫不夸张地说，对于个人VTuber来说，这是继Live2D、3D之后的一个梦想。这就是为什么能够和我的三个朋友一起去拍摄对我来说是一件大事。我想当你看到他们玩得开心时，你就能看到他们有多高兴。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.98g0p8stzend-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.98g0p8stzend-1024x575.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.98g0p8stzend-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.98g0p8stzend-300x168.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.98g0p8stzend-768x431.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.98g0p8stzend-jpg.webp 1137w" width="1024" height="575" /></a></p><p>当然，个人只要花钱就可以轻松租到一台，但这一次，我们用我们三个人制作的奥萨原创商品“奥萨咖喱”的销售收入，将我们三个人聚集在一起。这对于拍摄来说是非常有意义的。<br />插画家 Satsuki Henya、VS 歌手 Sayo Nanashino、美食和创意 Omu。虽然三人的目标不同，但《奥萨》的魅力就在于可以看到志同道合的创作者们聚在一起玩耍，一起前进。这个视频捕捉到了这一重大进步。<br />看来此时拍摄的镜头将来会上传，值得我们期待。</p><h2> 《调色板计划》原创动画PV </h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《调色板计划》原创动画PV" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ae20XvnYV4E?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>虚拟偶像团体<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@PaletteProject" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Palette Project</strong></a> （以下简称Palette Pro）全新宣传视频公开。这段非常详细的动画视频将 Parepro 现有成员的活动与刚刚加入的新研究生的活动联系起来。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.qzje3s7eooum-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.qzje3s7eooum-1024x577.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.qzje3s7eooum-1024x577.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.qzje3s7eooum-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.qzje3s7eooum-768x433.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.qzje3s7eooum-jpg.webp 1136w" width="1024" height="577" /></a></p><p> 5月17日至18日首次直播的六位练习生分别是<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@aizomeanela" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>蓝染阿奈拉</strong></a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@tsukimiyaao" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>月宫苍</strong></a>、夏木<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@nanagisamahalo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>真</strong></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@nihonbarekoko" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>郎</strong></a>、日本春心、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@mashiromomona" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>桃名真广</strong></a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@mutsuraboshinaru" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>六连星奈留</strong></a>。讲述了女孩们看到目前活跃的Pare Pro舞台后的感动，并为加入Pare Pro而努力的故事。从<a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLlTp7MW661kYspm0e1VIKza8VqccQlS0t" target="_blank" rel="noopener">预告片</a>来看，他们个个都有着独特的个性。非常期待广播和偶像活动。<br />另一方面，动画中出现的对现任Parepro成员<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@akatsukiclara" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Clara Akatsuki</strong></a>的采访相当有分量，令人印象深刻。<br /> “有很多很难的事情，我很沮丧，我哭了，但我觉得这真的很有趣！”<br />与一边思考眼泪的意义一边开始努力的练习生相比，可以感受到偶像们的感动。<br /> ParePro的吸引力在于您可以在YouTube上实时观看偶像在舞台上的战斗、成长和发光。你可以看到他们都在寻找和表达自己，大家齐心协力，与外界偶像互动，在粉丝的支持下成长，并以最好的现场表演发光发热。<br />如果您已经是 Parepro 的粉丝，或者您有兴趣并想尝试一下，那么现在您有机会看到 Kenkyusei 从头开始​​。一边追随实时偶像的成长故事，一边追随Pare Pro主创一代的成功，让人感觉很有趣的充满激情的PV。</p><h2> 【人气很高】重现静冈清爽的汉堡牛排，太好吃了！ ！ ！真是肉山啊！ ！ [VTuber烹饪/Shimomo Anon] [当地美食] </h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【人气很高】重现静冈清爽的汉堡牛排，太好吃了！ ！ ！真是肉山啊！ ！ [VTuber烹饪/Shimomo Anon] [当地美食]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-L2O0ILneGE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>前几天出现在<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N6rV73B0P0g" target="_blank" rel="noopener">加里本格五号开放校园</a>的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Shito_ANON" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Anon Shimomo</strong></a> 。这次，她将重新制作静冈著名的“泽中式”元骨汉堡牛排。想要完美地再现拥有这么多粉丝的汉堡牛排是很困难的，但是这次的《Kaze》似乎很令人满意，所以我想让你尝试模仿它作为食谱视频。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.dtokwnju4yv2-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.dtokwnju4yv2-1024x579.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.dtokwnju4yv2-1024x579.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.dtokwnju4yv2-300x170.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.dtokwnju4yv2-768x434.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.dtokwnju4yv2-jpg.webp 1136w" width="1024" height="579" /></a></p><p>我研究Sawayaka食谱并在烹饪时模仿它，在这样做时，味噌将最佳烹饪方法解释为知识。它包括一些琐事，例如如何使用冷冻西兰花以及使用碎肉中的脂肪的最佳方法，所以一旦您了解了它，您就会想亲自尝试一下。<br />此外，Shimo Anon 的大多数视频在摘要部分都包含了文字食谱，因此对于那些在制作视频时没有时间回顾视频的人来说非常有帮助。<br />成品视频看起来如此美味，是因为她长期以烹饪为主的VTuber活跃。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[漫画美食] 大美食！望月简单的蛋包饭来了……哇！感受生活！ [VTuber烹饪/Shimomo Anon] [复制食谱]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lrn8J3DZMpU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>我们还制作了以流行漫画“望月同学”为主题的巨型简单煎蛋卷饭。凭借扎实的厨艺和曾经制作过超高热量食物的疯狂厨神的手艺，他创造出了一道看起来美味可口的菜肴。他准确地介绍了美味的要点，并告诉人们如何实际做，展现了他作为厨师的承诺。<br />这个频道充满了对美味棕色食物的热爱和欣喜，只需看看缩略图列表就会激起您的食欲。这是一个充满吃的乐趣的频道，上传了很多视频，你可以在直播中观看烹饪过程。</p><h2>聚集在一起！愚蠢的自助武士斗兽场！ ！ ！ [有件事疯传] </h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="聚集在一起！愚蠢的自助武士斗兽场！ ！ ！ [有件事疯传]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/z_LbQchby0c?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-media-max-width="560"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja">停止！<br />自助不仅仅是省钱的方式！<br />这是与 Vongola Biango 的竞争，后者的面条和蛤蜊的比例相同！ <a href="https://t.co/GUMZkqTUI0">pic.twitter.com/GUMZkqTUI0</a></p><p> ——三重作丸<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f939.png" alt="🤹" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />视频 Vtuber (@MitamaSakumaru) <a href="https://twitter.com/MitamaSakumaru/status/1788155659831394344?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 5 月 8 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@mitamasakumaru" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Sanju Sakumaru</strong></a>发布了一张带有额外蛤蜊的 Vongole Bianco 的照片，引起了巨大的热议，他说自己做饭的乐趣不仅仅是省钱，而是能够做任何你想做的事情。我们收到了很多喜欢自己做饭的人的报价。<br />我把它命名为“愚蠢的自助武士”。我们正在介绍一些提交作品的照片，但它们是否可以食用、是否合理都是次要的，结果是一个充满“我可以做我想做的”精神的有趣的美食报道视频如果我自己做饭的话。”马苏。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.wb0axrdh3yrz-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.wb0axrdh3yrz-1024x573.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.wb0axrdh3yrz-1024x573.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.wb0axrdh3yrz-300x168.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.wb0axrdh3yrz-768x430.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.wb0axrdh3yrz-jpg.webp 1140w" width="1024" height="573" /></a></p><p>超级大的饭团、不需要连在一起的长长的环、看不到米的扇贝碗、大萝卜咖喱等等，不仅份量大，而且兴奋得让人想都尝尝他们都有。<br />在这个项目中，我们创建了罗马斗兽场的3D模型，并进入空间播放视频，这是只有VTuber才能拥有的有趣体验。我们毫不犹豫地使用技术。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【Jollof Rice】印象：僵尸饭很好吃！ ？ 【Fufu尼日利亚美食】" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Uh2jyoR-ohY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>它还触及了最近X上的热门话题，“一个印象派僵尸开始发布食物的照片。”这是因为那些发布类似垃圾邮件的帖子以获取印象的人被指出，如果他们上传自己国家的美食或地区以及生活在其中的人们的照片，这将是有意义的，并且可能会像病毒一样传播。用日语介绍民族美食的帖子数量不断增加，成为热门话题，这是独特而有意义的新闻流。<br />对此，佐久丸三重立即去吃尼日利亚菜肴Jollof Rice。轻盈的步法、高耸的触角以及融合现实与虚拟的活动方式，是三重作丸作为艺人的强项。</p><h2> [嘉宾：花生君] ELLE Kitchen ～Elle Teresa 的烹饪秀～ [POP YOURS 合作] </h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[嘉宾：花生君] ELLE Kitchen ～Elle Teresa 的烹饪秀～ [POP YOURS 合作]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KDSdgoIJOXA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>出现在嘻哈活动“POP YOURS”中的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Peanutskun" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Peanuts</strong></a>出现在说唱歌手Kan aka GAMI的频道<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@kankitchen_sstv" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kan Kitchen</a>中，并与说唱歌手Elle Teresa合作。在韩厨房，Peanut君之前曾与韩又名GAMI合作过，当时的谈话很友好。<br />另一方面，这一次，从头到尾都有一个独特的停顿，一个女孩和一个不同的存在的出现，使它成为一个奇怪的视频，让你以各种方式发笑。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.c29v4bfnvndg-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.c29v4bfnvndg-1024x574.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.c29v4bfnvndg-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.c29v4bfnvndg-300x168.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.c29v4bfnvndg-768x430.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.c29v4bfnvndg-jpg.webp 1137w" width="1024" height="574" /></a></p><p>花生君自称“Kigurumi”，并试图靠近他，但他太咄咄逼人，以至于吓坏了，这是典型的五岁男孩的表现。他略显失常的沟通方式非常适合笑声，而且这种氛围是《花生漫画》的长期粉丝所认同的。<br />同时，这次合作也表明了 Peanuts 在嘻哈界的知名度。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="干得好，让我们冥想一下吧？" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sIARC7GE0GU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Peanuts 的亮点在于，他会发出信息，筛选通过这次合作创造的新粉丝并 POP YOURS。从评论部分可以看出，以自己的节奏构建自己的世界的精神，出现在老式的 2D 视觉效果中，正是它对粉丝如此有吸引力的原因，但同时，没有人知道你在做什么这就是艺人花生的魅力。</p><h2> Sara Meidugahara《Monday the 13th》官方MV </h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sara Meidugahara《Monday the 13th》官方MV" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2I_alumYC1I?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>作为虚拟人类发行者活跃的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@meidogahara_sarasa" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Sara Meidugahara</strong></a>的新原创歌曲《Monday the 13th》已上传。这是一首略带怀旧基调的techno pop曲子，风格与女仆的风骚感完美契合。她的歌声有一种悠然轻快的感觉，非常有魅力，充满了女孩自由奔放的精神。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.8aiju9sn1006-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.8aiju9sn1006-1024x525.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.8aiju9sn1006-1024x525.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.8aiju9sn1006-300x154.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.8aiju9sn1006-768x394.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/5c908cbbdd088ade616db6dbe8614bf1-kix.8aiju9sn1006-jpg.webp 1138w" width="1024" height="525" /></a></p><p>从这段视频和直播中可以看出，Sarasora Meidugahara 作为虚拟人的视觉水平相当高，即使她实时移动，质量也很高。<br />她的另一个存在，与真人稍有不同，甚至是变形的动漫人物，与这首歌结合起来，感觉像是对“可爱”的新追求。</p><p>往期推荐文章请点击：<br /><a href="https://www.moguravr.com/category/vtuber-weekly-infomation/">必看！本周推荐VTuber</a></p><p>帖子这个<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-weekly-24-5-20/">视频太棒了！本周推荐的 VTuber 视频（截至 5 月 17 日）</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; 
我尝试体验“全息地球”的新领域作为虚拟宇宙的完美程度正在稳步提高https://www.moguravr.com/holo-earth-update-review-2024-5/ノンジャンル人生 Mon, 20 May 2024 07:13:43 +0000 VTuberホロライブメタバースホロアース https://www.moguravr.com/?p=251341 <p> Hololive Productions 运营公司 Cover Co., Ltd. 更新了元宇宙项目“Holo Earth”。 “另类城市 v1”作为新区域开放。在这篇文章中，我们将介绍游戏新增的功能[...]</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/holo-earth-update-review-2024-5/">我尝试体验“全息地球”新领域的帖子作为虚拟宇宙的完美程度不断提高，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p>运营<a href="https://hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hololive Productions</a>的<a href="https://cover-corp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cover Co., Ltd.</a>更新了元宇宙项目<strong>“</strong> <a href="https://holoearth.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Holo Earth</strong></a> <strong>”</strong> 。 <strong>“另类城市 v1”</strong>作为新区域开放。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.fei91wtj6y44-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.fei91wtj6y44-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.fei91wtj6y44-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.fei91wtj6y44-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.fei91wtj6y44-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>在这篇文章中，我们将介绍新添加的功能以及一些游戏玩法。</p><h2>未来派“另类城市v1”</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.c3isqvrde92n-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.c3isqvrde92n-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.c3isqvrde92n-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.c3isqvrde92n-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.c3isqvrde92n-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>新区域“另类城市v1”是在上一个版本中被标记为正在建设中并且没有任何内容的区域。然而，通过这次更新，城市景观已经完成，并且现在可以使用设施<strong>“ALTERMODE”和“ALT BEAUTYS”</strong> 。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.l09898n0e5ea-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.l09898n0e5ea-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.l09898n0e5ea-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.l09898n0e5ea-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.l09898n0e5ea-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.hhdc25hibmqv-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.hhdc25hibmqv-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.hhdc25hibmqv-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.hhdc25hibmqv-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.hhdc25hibmqv-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j02jemo88nip-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j02jemo88nip-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j02jemo88nip-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j02jemo88nip-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j02jemo88nip-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>当你在城市中漫步时，你会对未来空间产生非常美丽的印象。还算宽敞，不过除了这次新增的两个设施之外，其他东西都不能进去。不过，有些地方我觉得未来的更新中会添加一些东西。</p><h2> “ALTERMODE”让你协调你的时尚</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.hx0rdxqgwe6y-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.hx0rdxqgwe6y-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.hx0rdxqgwe6y-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.hx0rdxqgwe6y-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.hx0rdxqgwe6y-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>时装店“ALTERMODE”是可以购买虚拟角色服装的设施。本次更新添加的服装排列在玻璃柜中，色彩缤纷、可爱的展示吸引了你的眼球。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.103bnvdrwuun-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.103bnvdrwuun-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.103bnvdrwuun-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.103bnvdrwuun-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.103bnvdrwuun-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>可以购买的时尚单​​品包括<strong>外套、内衣、下装、袜子、鞋子和配饰</strong>，每件都可以单独购买。只需一件就能给您的印象带来很大的改变。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j2duypnc0wcg-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j2duypnc0wcg-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j2duypnc0wcg-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j2duypnc0wcg-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j2duypnc0wcg-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>您需要了解的一件事是，每种时尚单品都有自己的“库存”概念。当库存为0时，会显示“SOLDOUT”，您将无法再购买。<strong>当我本周初去时，有几件商品已经卖完了。</strong></p><p>按照官方的说法，库存会补货，不过以后的更新中似乎会增加“批号”，而且前期购买的物品都是有纪念意义的，所以大家一定要确保自己想要的东西尽快也是一手。</p><h2>改变你外表的“ALT BEAUTYS”</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.ctudf0q1bjrd-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.ctudf0q1bjrd-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.ctudf0q1bjrd-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.ctudf0q1bjrd-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.ctudf0q1bjrd-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> “ALT BEAUTYS”是一家拥有时尚沙龙<strong>“ALT STYLE”</strong>和诊所<strong>“ALT CLINIC”</strong>的设施。它位于中央大楼后面稍远的地方。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.nqhjdko2sl1t-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.nqhjdko2sl1t-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.nqhjdko2sl1t-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.nqhjdko2sl1t-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.nqhjdko2sl1t-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.eparvllqsyoq-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.eparvllqsyoq-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.eparvllqsyoq-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.eparvllqsyoq-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.eparvllqsyoq-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>在造型沙龙里，你可以改变发型、脸部零件和妆容。至于头发，你可以改变每个区块（前/侧/后），仅仅通过组合最初的发型，印象就会发生很大的变化。此外，您还可以购买新发型来打造自己的发型。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.on9fjs7jjl21-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.on9fjs7jjl21-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8